creator: Tabsquare Pte Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Use Tabsquare Console (Printer Console & Merchant Console) in your cafe or restaurant to inform cooking staff what to prepare from an order. Tabsquare Console communicates directly with tabsquare kiosk apps & some ordering partners like GPay and displays all necessary order information: items, modifiers and notes.

Features:
- Get orders to kitchen automatically, faster and with less errors.
- Never miss a new order using sound notifications.
- Less paper, less mess. Save and go green.
- Support EPSON Printers

Sleek design
Straight-forward user interface which requires zero training.

Seamless installation
Download and set up in an instant. Use the same merchant key you’ve been using for Tabsquare apps.
